{
    "comment_thread": {}, 
    "video_length": "PT8M47S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Good evening everybody.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First I want to tell you\nthat I never thought", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would be standing in front of you one day.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Above all, because\nI&#39;m not a sociologist", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or a scientist", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or a researcher.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In common language,\nyou can say I am a tagger.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Really, I never thought\nI would stand in front of you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I must say\nthat it got off to a bad start.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was born in a family", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that was quite poor,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "violent and particularly illiterate.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In my family nobody went to school", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "beyond the age of 14 year old.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To complete the picture,\nmy mom had me when she was 13 years old.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is quite young.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Further, she committed suicide\nwhen I was 5.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She was then 18.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This whole mess was explained\nto me when I was 14.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It did not go very well.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Concerning schooling,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "since we&#39;re at TEDx Universit\u00e9s,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was schooled quite late,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the age of 7.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The socialisation with the others kids\nwas quite difficult.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They soon started to scare me,\nI had almost never seen one,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "therefore I went to sit", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the back of the classroom", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or at least,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one teacher kindly guided me there", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was the last one to arrive.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I stayed at the back of the classroom", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "during all my school years.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Until the very last day.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was a teenager\nand my family explained to me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the mess in which I was born,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I of course became a drug addict.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With everything it implies:\ndelinquency, the fall,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "boom, boom, boom.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then I decided to revolt.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not that I decided to change the world", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or to lead a revolution, not at all.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t even try to change myself,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I thought it was already too late.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, I tried only one thing:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I tried to hope.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I convinced myself", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I could hope for much,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even that I could dream.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now dreaming is a great gift.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A very, very great gift.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Like the previous speaker said", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anyone who succeeded also hoped.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even those who failed also hoped.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Therefore it is a great gift.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In order to hope, to dream", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you must have a big hole somewhere,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a big emptiness inside.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First of all, you must give up.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You must give up your ideals.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You must give up your ideals.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ideals are rigid things,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stillborn,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sterile things.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They are like a dream\nthat was instilled to you from the outside.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In general,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ideals are sterile.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In order to dream,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you must allow some free space inside of you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you to try and give space to positive things", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that might happen to you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In order to dream, you must welcome", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what the real world has to offer\nand not what you would impose to it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In order to hope, you must somehow think:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe what is going to happen", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "will be better than what I had planned.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I did dream a lot.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From the back of the classroom.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I started doing graffiti,\nor the tag as we say,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was around 15 years old.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I never imagined\nit could become my job.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At that time, it was unthinkable.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In 1989, when I took my first spray", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can, I never thought it could become my job.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It wasn&#39;t even a job yet at that time,\nit did not exist as such", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You did it to have fun, to show off,\nto hit on girls a little bit.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I never had the idea\nof pursuing it as a career.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As a metaphor, it&#39;s a bit like saying", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that a teenager starts burgling", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in order to become a better locksmith.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, that does not exist.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I started, I never imagined", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that, 20 years later, in my town", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when policemen controlled me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I was painting,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they would stop to ask me for an autograph.\nThat happened.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t think that, 20 years later,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in Barcelona a judge\nwould discharge me for painting", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on his electricity equipment\nin his jurisdiction,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and even better, invite me to come back \nto make his city more beautiful.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That happened.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, I never thought it would.\nWhen I started to work with stencils,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it wasn&#39;t that long ago, in 2006,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even taggers", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would laugh at me and say", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;hey but that is used to decorate a kitchen!&quot;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would never have imagined.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At that time they would say\nthat this was no art.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And yet...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "yet...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happened.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happened notably", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "after the birth of my daughter,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "whose name is Nina,\nwhom you can see here,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I wanted to show my kid", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a positive face of her father", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and an optimistic view of life.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I wanted in a way", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to show her my best side.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to get used to it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happened.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happened: mayors from\nall over the world write to me today", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "-- well, their secretaries --\nto offer me walls to smear,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at their own costs.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, that&#39;s how it is.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It also happened that", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was paid some plane tickets to come", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and do a little tag\nin a corner of a street.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happened,\nyou have to get used to it.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now I have a memory lapse.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So all this to say that if one day", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "somebody considered you as an offbeat,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "abnormal,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe you were just singular.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And maybe if you were placed", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the back of the classroom,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it might make sense for you.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because in a sense\nwhat does being an artist mean", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if not dreaming?\nDreaming a little bit for others.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Dreaming for yourself;", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "dreaming about yourself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because art is somehow an odyssey.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a personal odyssey.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is giving birth to yourself.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Giving birth to the world.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s transforming a ramshackle door,\nas long as I&#39;m concerned,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with tags, stickers,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "something neglected,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a bit like an abandoned kid,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s transforming", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this useless and ugly thing", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into a pretty thing that people", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "want to appropriate,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to take care of,\nand to keep close to themselves.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s transforming", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the most useless thing", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into the most precious thing.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s what being an artist means.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In order to achieve that,\nyou must dream a lot.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You must dream\nand make people dream.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you must be somewhat a clown,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "somewhat a magician", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in order to entertain,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to impress.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Being an artist, in a sense,\nmeans dreaming for others.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Dreaming,\nbut from the back of the classroom.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if you too", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "were born with the wrong cards,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "were born with the wrong cards,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you were told to be abnormal,\ndon&#39;t believe it:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this means you were singular.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you were told\nthat you had your head in the clouds", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "while looking out the window,\nthinking of something else,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s just that you were dreaming,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and never give up\nyour dreams and passions,", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because dreams and passions create", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the most beautiful things in this world.", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }
